title: William Carabano 40th Birthday / Holiday Party
desc: Come celebrate my 40th birthday with me in style! Join 200 friends, family and I as we bring in a new decade with music, dancing, comedy, and more! Due to limited spacing, we offer three great options (Ages 21 & Over, ID Required:) 1) $10 ticket: Guarantees admission + one free drink. 2) $20 ticket: Guarantees admission to live show + one free drink. 3) $50 ticket: Guarantees admission to live show + one free BOTTLE of organic wine AND any three free food items from the menu we provide that night. List of performers performing at 9P - 10P and 11P - Midnight (more added each week:) // SINGERS & MUSICIANS // Chris Zurich (Neo Soul) Moriah Skye & Jade Zabric (R&B, Soul) // DANCERS // Boogie Babes (Samba Dancers, featuring Cookie & Bianca) Nati Castillo & Fofa Londono (Capoeiristas) // COMEDIANS // Alex Carabano (Comedian) 2 x Comedians to be added shortly Plus, a SUPER surprise headliner having his big comedy debut with us that night! DJ's include: Anthony Rizo (visualizemusic.com) Door by: Dave & Nigel Call me if you have any questions (347) 423-6896.
